4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed to prepare students for careers in AI and data science without any prior knowledge. With a duration of 16 weeks, the program includes three classes per week, limited to a maximum of 12 participants. Students will learn Python, SQL, and various machine learning algorithms, completing projects that mimic real-world challenges. The course is available in English and Spanish and culminates in a recognized certificate. Experienced instructors, including PhD holders, guide learners through this comprehensive curriculum. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop